00:00:26.201 --> 00:00:27.160 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:00:27.661 --> 00:00:29.162 line:90%
Prince Iksang has arrived.

00:00:31.373 --> 00:00:33.166 line:90%
Is his son with him as well?

00:00:34.459 --> 00:00:35.502 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:00:37.963 --> 00:00:39.798 line:90%
How is Prince Yeongan?

00:00:40.715 --> 00:00:44.553 line:90%
His condition has not improved,
so he will not be able to attend.

00:00:52.435 --> 00:00:54.563 line:90%
-You may leave.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

00:00:58.733 --> 00:01:02.404 line:90%
It seems that man, Gu-cheon, has failed.

00:01:05.240 --> 00:01:06.950 line:90%
People say

00:01:07.951 --> 00:01:11.246 line:90%
I took the throne because of a spirit.

00:01:12.330 --> 00:01:13.415 line:90%
Yet now they mock me,

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.461 line:90%
saying my throne will be shaken by it.

00:01:20.755 --> 00:01:22.924 line:90%
Which do you think is true?

00:01:39.065 --> 00:01:41.610 line:90%
We will know when we get there.

00:01:45.447 --> 00:01:49.618 line:90%
The royal affines and the kin officials.

00:01:49.701 --> 00:01:52.579 line:90%
Perform four ceremonial bows.

00:01:58.209 --> 00:02:00.378 line:90%
Bow.

00:02:00.879 --> 00:02:03.173 line:90%
Rise.

00:02:03.256 --> 00:02:05.550 line:90%
Bow.

00:02:06.468 --> 00:02:08.386 line:90%
Rise.

00:02:08.970 --> 00:02:11.139 line:90%
Bow.

00:02:11.765 --> 00:02:13.725 line:90%
Rise.

00:02:23.777 --> 00:02:25.779 line:90%
Next, the Crown Prince should offer wine,

00:02:25.862 --> 00:02:28.865 line:90%
praying for Your Majesty's longevity
and good health.

00:02:29.658 --> 00:02:31.993 line:90%
However, the seat is vacant.

00:02:32.494 --> 00:02:34.829 line:90%
-Perhaps this should be omitted--
-No.

00:02:36.831 --> 00:02:38.583 line:90%
This old body of mine

00:02:39.501 --> 00:02:42.837 line:90%
may not last
until another birthday banquet.

00:02:44.089 --> 00:02:46.549 line:90%
What do you think, Your Majesty?

00:02:50.971 --> 00:02:53.181 line:90%
As you wish, Mother.

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:07.487 line:90%
The eldest son of Prince Iksang,
step forward!

00:03:07.570 --> 00:03:10.156 line:90%
Prince Iksang, congratulations.

00:03:39.936 --> 00:03:42.439 line:90%
This is the cup of wine
offered by Prince Inha.

00:03:43.189 --> 00:03:46.776 line:90%
I pray for Your Majesty's longevity
and good health.

00:04:07.047 --> 00:04:08.131 line:90%
What is happening?

00:04:09.841 --> 00:04:11.718 line:90%
How did the door…

00:04:56.096 --> 00:04:58.515 line:90%
-Something is here.
-Your Majesty.

00:05:27.669 --> 00:05:28.586 line:90%
<i>Yes.</i>

00:05:30.463 --> 00:05:32.674 line:90%
<i>I knew you would return to me</i>
<i>in resentment</i>

00:05:33.883 --> 00:05:36.761 line:90%
<i>once I had tormented you.</i>

00:05:38.096 --> 00:05:39.305 line:90%
<i>Now,</i>

00:05:40.223 --> 00:05:41.850 line:90%
<i>what will you do?</i>

00:06:02.287 --> 00:06:03.746 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:06:15.592 --> 00:06:17.051 line:90%
Come to your senses!

00:06:18.636 --> 00:06:22.056 line:90%
Do you truly wish to kill someone
and become an ak-gwi?

00:06:26.936 --> 00:06:28.688 line:90%
You said becoming an ak-gwi after death

00:06:29.939 --> 00:06:32.066 line:90%
was the thing you feared the most.

00:06:38.072 --> 00:06:39.115 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:06:40.074 --> 00:06:42.368 line:90%
You are not to blame
for the death of your mother.

00:06:47.916 --> 00:06:50.835 line:90%
That gwi-mae has taken hold of you.

00:06:52.420 --> 00:06:53.880 line:90%
If you still cannot trust me,

00:06:55.423 --> 00:06:56.799 line:90%
I will uncover the truth.

00:06:58.051 --> 00:06:59.010 line:90%
Once I leave the palace,

00:06:59.093 --> 00:07:01.679 line:90%
I will find your mother's soul
and reveal the truth.

00:07:10.772 --> 00:07:11.814 line:90%
So let us

00:07:13.274 --> 00:07:15.193 line:90%
make it out of the palace alive.

00:07:59.904 --> 00:08:04.826 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:08:19.465 --> 00:08:21.801 line:90%
-Prince Inha!
-Prince Inha!

00:08:21.884 --> 00:08:24.512 line:90%
What is wrong with him?
What is happening to him?

00:08:24.595 --> 00:08:26.222 line:90%
-All of a sudden…
-Wake up!

00:08:26.723 --> 00:08:27.932 line:90%
Summon the physician!

00:08:28.016 --> 00:08:30.226 line:90%
-Send for the physician!
-Summon the physician!

00:08:30.727 --> 00:08:31.686 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:08:36.316 --> 00:08:38.359 line:90%
The child is flawed.

00:08:43.072 --> 00:08:45.825 line:90%
This must be disappointing for you,
Mother.

00:08:47.660 --> 00:08:49.329 line:90%
In such a frail state,

00:08:49.996 --> 00:08:53.958 line:90%
how could he ever withstand
the energy of the palace?

00:08:58.254 --> 00:09:01.841 line:90%
You would need to become
a better judge of character.

00:09:03.634 --> 00:09:05.303 line:90%
Continue the banquet.

00:09:05.803 --> 00:09:07.972 line:90%
Let the music continue!

00:09:09.098 --> 00:09:11.142 line:90%
Attend to Prince Inha at once!

00:09:48.805 --> 00:09:50.348 line:90%
No.

00:10:01.776 --> 00:10:02.652 line:90%
Princess.

00:10:03.736 --> 00:10:04.737 line:90%
Princess!

00:10:27.218 --> 00:10:28.344 line:90%
Have you lost your mind?

00:10:29.137 --> 00:10:31.180 line:90%
I told you never to set foot in there.

00:10:31.681 --> 00:10:33.683 line:90%
You never listen to me.

00:10:35.351 --> 00:10:37.061 line:90%
I saved you, yet you reproach me.

00:10:37.854 --> 00:10:40.022 line:90%
You could have died and become a spirit.

00:10:40.523 --> 00:10:43.568 line:90%
-Was I supposed to just stand by?
-Never do that again.

00:10:43.651 --> 00:10:45.903 line:90%
Whether I become a spirit
or a wandering soul.

00:10:46.654 --> 00:10:50.366 line:90%
I never want to see anyone die
because of me again.

00:11:06.257 --> 00:11:07.842 line:90%
If you insist,

00:11:08.968 --> 00:11:10.595 line:90%
I will never do it again.

00:11:12.013 --> 00:11:13.055 line:90%
I cannot

00:11:14.724 --> 00:11:16.893 line:90%
bring myself to go in there again either.

00:11:17.727 --> 00:11:19.228 line:90%
I was terrified.

00:11:23.524 --> 00:11:24.400 line:90%
It must have been

00:11:26.235 --> 00:11:28.070 line:90%
a difficult time for you.

00:12:15.868 --> 00:12:17.245 line:90%
No such thing as spirits.

00:12:18.829 --> 00:12:19.997 line:90%
Mother.

00:12:20.540 --> 00:12:22.208 line:90%
Spirits do not exist.

00:12:24.252 --> 00:12:26.087 line:90%
Spirits do not exist.

00:12:27.755 --> 00:12:28.589 line:90%
Mother?

00:12:31.217 --> 00:12:33.052 line:90%
It is your father who is the spirit.

00:12:58.369 --> 00:12:59.203 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:13:04.125 --> 00:13:06.294 line:90%
What are you doing there?

00:13:06.877 --> 00:13:08.004 line:90%
How is your fever?

00:13:10.798 --> 00:13:12.592 line:90%
Why open the door without asking?

00:13:15.886 --> 00:13:17.305 line:90%
You still have that temper.

00:13:25.563 --> 00:13:26.439 line:90%
Miss Saeng-gang!

00:13:27.356 --> 00:13:28.774 line:90%
Are you up?

00:13:29.525 --> 00:13:31.527 line:90%
What is going on?

00:13:34.363 --> 00:13:37.742 line:90%
I thought Gu-cheon was dead,
yet he is walking around alive.

00:13:38.326 --> 00:13:42.663 line:90%
I thought you were fine, but you slept
for three days and nights as if dead.

00:13:42.747 --> 00:13:44.957 line:90%
-I slept for three days?
-Yes.

00:13:45.041 --> 00:13:46.626 line:90%
Have these first.

00:13:46.709 --> 00:13:49.253 line:90%
I begged the female physician
for this herbal medicine

00:13:49.337 --> 00:13:51.672 line:90%
and snuck these rice cakes
from Saenggwabang.

00:13:51.756 --> 00:13:54.050 line:90%
You have not eaten at all for three days.

00:13:55.051 --> 00:13:56.761 line:90%
Here. Please eat.

00:13:58.012 --> 00:13:59.096 line:90%
Thank you.

00:14:07.730 --> 00:14:10.733 line:90%
But why did you bring so many rice cakes?

00:14:11.651 --> 00:14:15.863 line:90%
Gu-cheon has not eaten for three days
either, so I brought his share.

00:14:15.946 --> 00:14:17.531 line:90%
But he just left.

00:14:17.615 --> 00:14:19.492 line:90%
Looks like he has no luck with food.

00:14:19.992 --> 00:14:21.535 line:90%
Is he not even hungry?

00:14:36.550 --> 00:14:39.387 line:90%
After three days without food,
it tastes even better.

00:14:40.554 --> 00:14:41.722 line:90%
Are you not going to eat?

00:14:44.892 --> 00:14:46.435 line:90%
I have no appetite.

00:14:46.936 --> 00:14:48.145 line:90%
You eat it all.

00:14:51.482 --> 00:14:53.067 line:90%
You should eat too.

00:14:54.735 --> 00:14:59.156 line:90%
You need to eat to work. Do not forget
what I found in the royal guard's place.

00:15:00.199 --> 00:15:02.243 line:90%
I will handle that myself,

00:15:02.326 --> 00:15:04.787 line:90%
so you need not concern yourself,
Your Highness.

00:15:05.538 --> 00:15:06.706 line:90%
"Your Highness"?

00:15:08.416 --> 00:15:10.876 line:90%
Why? What?

00:15:14.422 --> 00:15:15.756 line:90%
You seem to have changed.

00:15:27.768 --> 00:15:31.605 line:90%
By the way, where is what you found
at the royal guard's residence?

00:15:33.441 --> 00:15:37.027 line:90%
The Most Favored Lady of the Court
made this for the child she was carrying.

00:15:40.823 --> 00:15:43.701 line:90%
Do you think this could ease
her resentment?

00:15:45.077 --> 00:15:46.746 line:90%
It may be possible,

00:15:46.829 --> 00:15:49.206 line:90%
but it will take a lot of preparation.

00:15:50.040 --> 00:15:51.667 line:90%
She is no ordinary spirit.

00:15:52.877 --> 00:15:55.588 line:90%
She is a won-gwi
and has killed for 30 years.

00:15:57.590 --> 00:16:01.010 line:90%
Oh, right. Where did you get
that lightning-struck jujube wood?

00:16:01.969 --> 00:16:05.431 line:90%
Oh. A jujube tree inside the palace
was struck by lightning.

00:16:06.724 --> 00:16:08.434 line:90%
Did it help at all?

00:16:10.060 --> 00:16:11.854 line:90%
It was a great help.

00:16:11.937 --> 00:16:13.522 line:90%
And it will continue to be.

00:16:14.023 --> 00:16:15.232 line:90%
Then

00:16:16.108 --> 00:16:18.319 line:90%
you could at least say thank you.

00:16:18.986 --> 00:16:20.946 line:90%
I believe I have helped you in many ways.

00:16:21.030 --> 00:16:25.326 line:90%
Can you not see that kind of showing off
kills all my gratitude?

00:16:25.409 --> 00:16:27.328 line:90%
How is that showing off?

00:16:27.411 --> 00:16:29.705 line:90%
I deserve a word of thanks.

00:16:30.206 --> 00:16:32.374 line:90%
I nearly died
handling your family's affairs.

00:16:32.458 --> 00:16:33.834 line:90%
A word of thanks? Ridiculous.

00:16:33.918 --> 00:16:36.212 line:90%
Do you want recognition that badly?

00:16:36.879 --> 00:16:39.006 line:90%
-Good grief.
-Good heavens.

00:16:41.634 --> 00:16:42.760 line:90%
Forget it.

00:16:44.053 --> 00:16:46.430 line:90%
You do not need to thank me.

00:16:46.514 --> 00:16:48.516 line:90%
Just say thank you to Ggeomeoksali.

00:16:50.059 --> 00:16:52.520 line:90%
It saved you from the gwi-mae in the well.

00:16:53.771 --> 00:16:54.688 line:90%
Did it?

00:16:54.772 --> 00:16:57.233 line:90%
No wonder I have not seen it
these past few days.

00:16:57.316 --> 00:16:59.568 line:90%
It fell into the well
while fighting the gwi-mae.

00:17:00.194 --> 00:17:01.195 line:90%
Oh dear.

00:17:01.737 --> 00:17:02.905 line:90%
Good riddance.

00:17:06.367 --> 00:17:07.743 line:90%
How heartless of you!

00:17:07.827 --> 00:17:11.455 line:90%
I do not do foolish things
like growing attached to gwi-mae.

00:17:11.956 --> 00:17:14.667 line:90%
Let us just focus
on how to banish the pond spirit.

00:17:26.679 --> 00:17:27.513 line:90%
What is wrong?

00:17:28.472 --> 00:17:29.306 line:90%
Well…

00:17:34.645 --> 00:17:38.566 line:90%
<i>when I crossed over to the other side,</i>
<i>I came face-to-face with the pond spirit.</i>

00:17:41.277 --> 00:17:43.988 line:90%
<i>It clawed at my back</i>
<i>and drained my energy,</i>

00:17:45.656 --> 00:17:48.576 line:90%
<i>but you pulled the rope just in time,</i>
<i>and I was freed from it.</i>

00:17:52.162 --> 00:17:53.163 line:90%
<i>"Clawed"?</i>

00:18:03.716 --> 00:18:04.842 line:90%
What is the matter?

00:18:12.224 --> 00:18:14.560 line:90%
The pond spirit that consumed your soul…

00:18:17.396 --> 00:18:19.398 line:90%
must be regaining its power.

00:18:20.733 --> 00:18:22.401 line:90%
<i>The curse that faltered for a moment</i>

00:18:22.902 --> 00:18:24.445 line:90%
<i>will grow stronger again.</i>

00:18:25.404 --> 00:18:26.405 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:18:27.239 --> 00:18:29.283 line:90%
The physician attending
Prince Yeongan says

00:18:29.950 --> 00:18:32.369 line:90%
you must prepare yourself for the worst.

00:18:45.466 --> 00:18:46.508 line:90%
Why…

00:18:57.144 --> 00:19:01.482 line:90%
I am not sure if we should
fight the pond spirit on impulse.

00:19:02.858 --> 00:19:06.528 line:90%
Prince Yeongan
will not make it through the night.

00:19:07.029 --> 00:19:10.115 line:90%
The lingering curse
must have pushed his body to the limit.

00:19:11.367 --> 00:19:12.534 line:90%
We have no time to waste.

00:19:20.459 --> 00:19:21.543 line:90%
Can you not hear it?

00:19:22.086 --> 00:19:23.003 line:90%
That sound?

00:19:38.852 --> 00:19:40.145 line:90%
Be careful.

00:19:42.064 --> 00:19:44.525 line:90%
I will not save someone
who does not even thank me.

00:19:45.025 --> 00:19:46.318 line:90%
Still holding onto it?

00:20:27.735 --> 00:20:28.777 line:90%
My baby…

00:20:47.046 --> 00:20:48.172 line:90%
<i>Can you shoot arrows?</i>

00:20:48.255 --> 00:20:51.467 line:90%
<i>Everyone tried to stop me</i>
<i>because I am a princess, but I insisted.</i>

00:20:51.550 --> 00:20:53.135 line:90%
<i>I learned it from my father.</i>

00:20:53.719 --> 00:20:55.679 line:90%
<i>So you have been odd</i>
<i>since you were little.</i>

00:20:56.346 --> 00:20:58.891 line:90%
<i>The baby's shirt</i>
<i>the Most Favored Lady of the Court made.</i>

00:20:58.974 --> 00:21:00.809 line:90%
<i>Take a thread stained with my blood.</i>

00:21:01.727 --> 00:21:04.104 line:90%
<i>Wrap this thread around an arrow.</i>
<i>Strike the spirit.</i>

00:21:04.188 --> 00:21:06.356 line:90%
<i>It will weaken its resentment.</i>

00:21:07.524 --> 00:21:08.358 line:90%
Here.

00:21:11.070 --> 00:21:12.946 line:90%
<i>When the baby stops crying,</i>

00:21:13.447 --> 00:21:14.865 line:90%
<i>shoot the arrow.</i>

00:21:17.326 --> 00:21:19.203 line:90%
<i>Her resentment over false accusation</i>

00:21:19.703 --> 00:21:22.664 line:90%
<i>and the grief of losing her child</i>
<i>need to be eased.</i>

00:22:00.494 --> 00:22:04.289 line:90%
Killing those of royal blood
will not bring your baby back.

00:22:04.873 --> 00:22:07.584 line:90%
So let go of your resentment
and pass on to the afterlife.

00:22:08.544 --> 00:22:12.381 line:90%
Free yourself from this hellish palace!

00:22:48.458 --> 00:22:49.793 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:22:49.877 --> 00:22:51.461 line:90%
Prince Yeongan has awakened.

00:22:51.545 --> 00:22:52.921 line:90%
What?

00:22:55.174 --> 00:22:57.384 line:90%
Do you mean he is improving?

00:22:57.467 --> 00:23:00.888 line:90%
Not merely improving, but a full recovery.

00:23:01.388 --> 00:23:05.517 line:90%
<i>The feng shui master His Majesty brought</i>
<i>seems to have banished the pond spirit.</i>

00:23:09.897 --> 00:23:10.731 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:23:17.696 --> 00:23:19.364 line:90%
Father.

00:23:25.078 --> 00:23:26.121 line:90%
Yes.

00:23:34.963 --> 00:23:39.134 line:90%
<i>He ended the curse</i>
<i>that has endured for 30 years?</i>

00:23:43.472 --> 00:23:44.723 line:90%
But…

00:23:47.392 --> 00:23:49.436 line:90%
that feng shui master.

00:23:50.270 --> 00:23:53.232 line:90%
How did he drive off the pond spirit?

00:23:54.691 --> 00:23:56.777 line:90%
I am not sure, Your Majesty.

00:23:57.277 --> 00:23:59.363 line:90%
While banishing the pond spirit,

00:23:59.446 --> 00:24:03.033 line:90%
he must have learned its true identity.

00:24:04.493 --> 00:24:06.411 line:90%
That man knows the secret.

00:24:06.495 --> 00:24:09.665 line:90%
He knows how that lowly maidservant
became a won-gwi.

00:24:10.791 --> 00:24:13.752 line:90%
We must silence him.

00:24:21.468 --> 00:24:24.137 line:90%
<i>The pond spirit has been banished.</i>

00:24:26.056 --> 00:24:27.140 line:90%
Yes.

00:24:29.393 --> 00:24:30.686 line:90%
So it seems.

00:24:31.186 --> 00:24:33.272 line:90%
Since I carried out your orders,

00:24:33.772 --> 00:24:35.816 line:90%
I deserve a reward, do I not?

00:24:44.157 --> 00:24:45.367 line:90%
Before that…

00:25:03.552 --> 00:25:04.636 line:90%
<i>Father,</i>

00:25:05.470 --> 00:25:07.222 line:90%
the palace frightens me.

00:25:07.306 --> 00:25:08.473 line:90%
Frightens you?

00:25:08.557 --> 00:25:11.393 line:90%
Who would dare frighten a princess?

00:25:12.561 --> 00:25:15.355 line:90%
I keep hearing strange sounds.

00:25:17.691 --> 00:25:19.276 line:90%
Saeng-gang, come here.

00:25:22.029 --> 00:25:25.032 line:90%
Here. Carry this with you.

00:25:25.115 --> 00:25:26.950 line:90%
If you do so,

00:25:28.035 --> 00:25:30.537 line:90%
this bell will ward off
those strange sounds.

00:25:39.004 --> 00:25:40.672 line:90%
Thanks to you, he lived.

00:25:42.007 --> 00:25:43.216 line:90%
Thank you.

00:25:48.597 --> 00:25:51.475 line:90%
I did not do this
to be praised like a child.

00:25:54.436 --> 00:25:55.354 line:90%
Very well.

00:25:56.938 --> 00:26:00.233 line:90%
Then what reward do you desire?

00:26:00.859 --> 00:26:03.236 line:90%
First, allow Gu-cheon to leave the palace.

00:26:04.696 --> 00:26:06.365 line:90%
Of course I will.

00:26:06.448 --> 00:26:07.783 line:90%
Without harming him.

00:26:08.658 --> 00:26:11.536 line:90%
That is my humble request.

00:26:21.129 --> 00:26:23.423 line:90%
Why are you not packing your things?

00:26:25.509 --> 00:26:28.804 line:90%
I have nothing on me. All I need
is the lightning-struck jujube wood.

00:26:33.183 --> 00:26:36.311 line:90%
You are leaving the palace,
yet you do not look happy.

00:26:37.562 --> 00:26:38.397 line:90%
It is just…

00:26:41.191 --> 00:26:42.526 line:90%
something feels off.

00:26:44.486 --> 00:26:45.862 line:90%
What do you mean?

00:26:46.363 --> 00:26:49.908 line:90%
Has Prince Yeongan truly recovered?
Is he completely well?

00:26:50.450 --> 00:26:52.035 line:90%
That is what I was told.

00:26:53.078 --> 00:26:55.455 line:90%
And how is your wound?

00:26:56.623 --> 00:26:58.542 line:90%
The pain is gone.

00:26:59.876 --> 00:27:01.128 line:90%
What is it?

00:27:02.879 --> 00:27:05.674 line:90%
It was not a spirit
that could be banished so easily.

00:27:06.216 --> 00:27:09.761 line:90%
A won-gwi that had killed the princes
of the East Palace for 30 years.

00:27:10.303 --> 00:27:13.181 line:90%
Four sons of the late King
and three sons of the present King.

00:27:14.391 --> 00:27:16.226 line:90%
For a won-gwi that killed seven,

00:27:17.394 --> 00:27:19.855 line:90%
it was too weak.

00:27:21.148 --> 00:27:22.107 line:90%
Are you sure…

00:27:24.359 --> 00:27:27.112 line:90%
those princes were killed
by the pond spirit?

00:27:27.863 --> 00:27:29.781 line:90%
If it was not the pond spirit,

00:27:30.615 --> 00:27:31.575 line:90%
then what was it?

00:27:35.745 --> 00:27:36.663 line:90%
I suppose…

00:27:37.581 --> 00:27:40.292 line:90%
I thought it would be hard enough
to put my life at risk.

00:27:41.793 --> 00:27:44.880 line:90%
But now that it is easily resolved,
all sorts of thoughts come to mind.

00:27:45.672 --> 00:27:49.301 line:90%
Good heavens, I must be out of my mind.
Completely out of my mind.

00:27:50.594 --> 00:27:53.889 line:90%
So once you leave the palace,
will you return to the temple?

00:27:53.972 --> 00:27:55.182 line:90%
Do you think I am mad?

00:27:56.349 --> 00:27:58.518 line:90%
I am still thinking about where to go.

00:28:01.062 --> 00:28:02.189 line:90%
And what will you do?

00:28:02.689 --> 00:28:04.524 line:90%
Did you find who did it to your mother?

00:28:08.612 --> 00:28:10.155 line:90%
It can only be that person.

00:28:33.053 --> 00:28:36.515 line:90%
You are the daughter
of the banished Third Senior Consort Han.

00:28:37.015 --> 00:28:39.309 line:90%
What brings you to the palace, Princess?

00:28:39.893 --> 00:28:44.105 line:90%
I have brought a gift to celebrate
the 70th birthday of Your Majesty.

00:28:45.190 --> 00:28:47.734 line:90%
It is quite modest compared to the others.

00:28:48.235 --> 00:28:51.363 line:90%
You came all this way for nothing.

00:28:52.822 --> 00:28:56.034 line:90%
I never permitted you to enter the palace.

00:28:56.117 --> 00:28:58.537 line:90%
Father granted permission.

00:28:58.620 --> 00:28:59.496 line:90%
What did you say?

00:28:59.579 --> 00:29:01.748 line:90%
His Majesty did so without consulting me?

00:29:02.249 --> 00:29:04.876 line:90%
Even when your mother was banished
for her crime?

00:29:04.960 --> 00:29:07.295 line:90%
You mean the court lady incident
in the salt store?

00:29:07.379 --> 00:29:10.131 line:90%
You framed my mother
and cast her out to cover it up.

00:29:10.715 --> 00:29:12.300 line:90%
You must have feared

00:29:12.384 --> 00:29:15.470 line:90%
the Most Favored Lady of the Court's death
would come to light.

00:29:15.554 --> 00:29:19.724 line:90%
The shameful secret of Your Majesty,
tied to the pond spirit.

00:29:26.106 --> 00:29:30.318 line:90%
You burst in
and speak nothing but nonsense.

00:29:31.027 --> 00:29:35.657 line:90%
Your mother was banished
for burying a cursed object.

00:29:35.740 --> 00:29:39.452 line:90%
-She denied her guilt to the very end--
-Is that why you killed my mother?

00:29:42.414 --> 00:29:45.458 line:90%
As she kept pleading with Father
for her life,

00:29:46.209 --> 00:29:48.753 line:90%
did you fear that your sin,
buried in the salt storehouse,

00:29:50.338 --> 00:29:52.507 line:90%
the serpent's cast skin, would be exposed?

00:29:52.591 --> 00:29:56.636 line:90%
Is it your upbringing outside the palace,
or your baseborn mother?

00:29:58.388 --> 00:30:00.432 line:90%
You have truly lost your mind.

00:30:00.515 --> 00:30:03.393 line:90%
How dare you make
such absurd accusations against me!

00:30:06.354 --> 00:30:07.439 line:90%
Open the gift.

00:30:17.616 --> 00:30:19.409 line:90%
I made the same sweets

00:30:19.909 --> 00:30:22.454 line:90%
my mother received from the palace
the day before she died.

00:30:30.629 --> 00:30:33.590 line:90%
<i>Not only the taste</i>
<i>but also the ingredients are the same.</i>

00:30:34.174 --> 00:30:35.467 line:90%
Please try some.

00:30:58.698 --> 00:31:01.993 line:90%
Who on earth told you such lies?

00:31:02.494 --> 00:31:06.873 line:90%
I had no part in the deaths of your mother
and the Most Favored Lady of the Court.

00:31:07.374 --> 00:31:10.335 line:90%
How could you possibly know
of events from…

00:31:13.004 --> 00:31:15.965 line:90%
Is that what you heard from Gu-cheon,
that feng shui master?

00:31:17.592 --> 00:31:21.346 line:90%
I should have taught that bastard sooner

00:31:21.429 --> 00:31:25.600 line:90%
what becomes of those
who lie in the palace.

00:31:27.060 --> 00:31:28.311 line:90%
It means death.

00:31:36.069 --> 00:31:39.406 line:90%
Now tell me what you have learned
about the pond spirit.

00:31:39.489 --> 00:31:40.699 line:90%
The pond spirit?

00:31:41.282 --> 00:31:42.367 line:90%
What is that?

00:31:42.450 --> 00:31:46.162 line:90%
Do you mean your grandfather
who drowned while bathing in the summer?

00:31:49.708 --> 00:31:51.000 line:90%
Throw him into a chest.

00:31:58.466 --> 00:32:03.847 line:90%
<i>In this austere palace,</i>
<i>only death awaits those who lie.</i>

00:32:03.930 --> 00:32:05.557 line:90%
Just like your mother.

00:32:08.268 --> 00:32:09.477 line:90%
I will return

00:32:10.603 --> 00:32:11.813 line:90%
those very words to you.

00:32:18.695 --> 00:32:21.906 line:90%
This is the baby's first shirt
the Most Favored Lady of the Court made.

00:32:22.407 --> 00:32:24.284 line:90%
You gave this to the royal guard

00:32:24.367 --> 00:32:26.578 line:90%
and made him falsely claim
the child was his.

00:32:28.079 --> 00:32:33.293 line:90%
-What are you--
-The Most Favored Lady of the Court.

00:32:34.252 --> 00:32:37.130 line:90%
You framed her and wiped out
the late King's bloodline.

00:32:38.131 --> 00:32:39.966 line:90%
The late King's bloodline?

00:32:40.467 --> 00:32:43.720 line:90%
That lowly maidservant
who took up with a mere royal guard?

00:32:43.803 --> 00:32:45.263 line:90%
Why did you go that far?

00:32:46.139 --> 00:32:48.683 line:90%
Unlike the other concubines
favored by the King,

00:32:48.767 --> 00:32:51.603 line:90%
you framed and killed
the Most Favored Lady of the Court. Why?

00:32:55.023 --> 00:32:56.649 line:90%
Out of jealousy?

00:33:02.781 --> 00:33:03.907 line:90%
Jealousy?

00:33:10.914 --> 00:33:12.874 line:90%
Did you say jealousy?

00:33:12.957 --> 00:33:17.045 line:90%
Toward that lowborn wench?

00:33:19.672 --> 00:33:22.467 line:90%
She once lived as a household slave
of my family.

00:33:22.550 --> 00:33:26.429 line:90%
And I was the one who allowed her
into the palace as a maidservant.

00:33:26.513 --> 00:33:27.722 line:90%
And I was jealous of her?

00:33:27.806 --> 00:33:29.808 line:90%
Nonsense!

00:33:35.063 --> 00:33:40.568 line:90%
I come from a long line of nobles!

00:33:41.194 --> 00:33:43.404 line:90%
But for years,

00:33:43.988 --> 00:33:49.452 line:90%
I was scorned by the late King
for bearing no child.

00:33:49.536 --> 00:33:54.040 line:90%
Yet that lowly slave won
His Majesty's favor and bore him a child!

00:33:55.124 --> 00:33:57.293 line:90%
I could not accept it.

00:33:57.794 --> 00:34:02.215 line:90%
I could accept concubines
from noble households and their children.

00:34:03.174 --> 00:34:06.344 line:90%
Yet the bloodline
carried by that lowborn woman

00:34:06.427 --> 00:34:11.516 line:90%
had to be cut off, by any means necessary.

00:34:13.768 --> 00:34:15.937 line:90%
Is that why you falsely accused her?

00:34:16.437 --> 00:34:17.856 line:90%
That is right!

00:34:18.857 --> 00:34:20.900 line:90%
I had that wretch tortured

00:34:21.734 --> 00:34:26.281 line:90%
and destroyed that filthy bloodline
in her womb!

00:34:32.412 --> 00:34:33.329 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:34:39.460 --> 00:34:40.545 line:90%
I heard you clearly.

00:34:41.546 --> 00:34:45.008 line:90%
Killing the Most Favored Lady of the Court
and the child of the late King.

00:34:46.092 --> 00:34:47.385 line:90%
You confessed to it.

00:34:50.054 --> 00:34:51.097 line:90%
What?

00:34:51.598 --> 00:34:54.684 line:90%
I will make this public
before Father and the ministers.

00:34:56.603 --> 00:34:58.521 line:90%
And you stated clearly earlier

00:34:58.605 --> 00:35:01.774 line:90%
that only death awaits those who lie.

00:35:03.735 --> 00:35:08.448 line:90%
Then tell me, Your Majesty.
What would death mean to you?

00:35:08.948 --> 00:35:12.076 line:90%
It would mean losing the palace,
which is everything to you.

00:35:15.163 --> 00:35:19.250 line:90%
All that power you have enjoyed
and the home you have lived in.

00:35:20.543 --> 00:35:21.711 line:90%
I will take it all away.

00:35:25.673 --> 00:35:29.427 line:90%
And how would you…

00:35:30.011 --> 00:35:33.932 line:90%
Who would ever believe
someone of such low birth,

00:35:34.015 --> 00:35:37.727 line:90%
banished from the palace?

00:35:40.104 --> 00:35:41.230 line:90%
I know that well.

00:35:42.815 --> 00:35:46.819 line:90%
Who would listen
to a mere princess like me?

00:35:56.287 --> 00:36:00.458 line:90%
Your voice was loud enough
for everyone to hear.

00:36:02.210 --> 00:36:03.044 line:90%
Now,

00:36:04.837 --> 00:36:06.297 line:90%
will you kill these people

00:36:06.798 --> 00:36:10.093 line:90%
and bury them like the court ladies
in the salt storehouse?

00:36:13.012 --> 00:36:15.598 line:90%
You will need a lot of jars
for their bones.

00:36:17.016 --> 00:36:17.850 line:90%
Let us go.

00:36:35.910 --> 00:36:37.245 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:36:43.334 --> 00:36:45.294 line:90%
I cannot look away for even a moment.

00:36:45.795 --> 00:36:47.714 line:90%
Why are you lying there all beaten up?

00:36:59.183 --> 00:37:01.352 line:90%
What trouble did you cause

00:37:02.311 --> 00:37:04.605 line:90%
that Her Majesty the Queen Dowager
wants you dead?

00:37:06.315 --> 00:37:08.359 line:90%
I thought it was His Majesty
who ordered this.

00:37:09.193 --> 00:37:11.988 line:90%
To see whether I could keep a secret.

00:37:14.073 --> 00:37:15.408 line:90%
Since you are so certain,

00:37:16.117 --> 00:37:18.494 line:90%
denying it would be pointless.

00:37:22.331 --> 00:37:24.292 line:90%
Then why do you spare me?

00:37:26.627 --> 00:37:29.005 line:90%
The Princess pleaded earnestly
with His Majesty

00:37:30.089 --> 00:37:33.134 line:90%
to let you leave the palace unharmed.

00:37:34.302 --> 00:37:36.846 line:90%
She must have known this would happen.

00:37:44.937 --> 00:37:46.564 line:90%
Your pass to leave the palace.

00:37:49.567 --> 00:37:50.985 line:90%
And this is your compensation.

00:37:53.279 --> 00:37:54.864 line:90%
Watch your mouth.

00:37:55.364 --> 00:37:57.950 line:90%
All eight provinces of Joseon
are in His Majesty's grasp.

00:38:22.892 --> 00:38:25.645 line:90%
They do not let me go so easily.

00:38:28.231 --> 00:38:30.024 line:90%
Still, it is over now.

00:39:06.561 --> 00:39:07.770 line:90%
I saw nothing.

00:39:07.854 --> 00:39:10.523 line:90%
I did not see anything. Nothing at all.

00:39:18.364 --> 00:39:19.198 line:90%
For heaven's sake.

00:39:41.971 --> 00:39:44.182 line:90%
I have repaid my debt to you
for saving me.

00:39:45.892 --> 00:39:46.934 line:90%
Take care.

00:40:09.332 --> 00:40:13.502 line:90%
I will give you some of my Yang energy.
Just enough for you to recover.

00:40:22.887 --> 00:40:24.639 line:90%
Let go! That is enough, damn it!

00:40:25.139 --> 00:40:25.973 line:90%
Enough!

00:40:52.667 --> 00:40:54.210 line:90%
You do not look well.

00:40:55.461 --> 00:40:56.587 line:90%
Are you ill?

00:40:57.880 --> 00:41:01.300 line:90%
I suppose working alongside Gu-cheon
has worn me out.

00:41:03.052 --> 00:41:06.973 line:90%
And last night, you caused quite a scene
at the Queen Dowager's residence,

00:41:07.682 --> 00:41:09.100 line:90%
so it is only natural.

00:41:09.600 --> 00:41:12.979 line:90%
What will you do about the Queen Dowager?

00:41:14.105 --> 00:41:16.691 line:90%
Is that why you came to see me
this early in the morning?

00:41:17.191 --> 00:41:18.150 line:90%
No.

00:41:18.234 --> 00:41:22.280 line:90%
I wanted to make sure
that Gu-cheon left the palace safely.

00:41:26.367 --> 00:41:28.327 line:90%
You worry about him too much.

00:41:29.537 --> 00:41:31.247 line:90%
He must have left the palace.

00:41:31.872 --> 00:41:34.083 line:90%
He should be on his way by now.

00:41:34.166 --> 00:41:35.918 line:90%
And he saved my son.

00:41:38.838 --> 00:41:41.132 line:90%
I have no intention of harming

00:41:42.425 --> 00:41:44.510 line:90%
the one who saved my child.

00:41:46.429 --> 00:41:47.805 line:90%
Do not worry.

00:41:50.099 --> 00:41:51.475 line:90%
By the way,

00:41:52.143 --> 00:41:55.980 line:90%
I did not expect that man
to deal with the pond spirit so easily.

00:41:57.940 --> 00:41:59.025 line:90%
Indeed.

00:41:59.108 --> 00:42:01.110 line:90%
Even Gu-cheon found it strange.

00:42:01.193 --> 00:42:04.488 line:90%
He asked if it was truly the pond spirit
that killed the princes.

00:42:06.866 --> 00:42:07.825 line:90%
Father.

00:42:09.702 --> 00:42:14.457 line:90%
How did the Crown Prince,
the first son of the late King, pass away?

00:42:19.462 --> 00:42:22.006 line:90%
-Your Highness!
-What is going on?

00:42:22.506 --> 00:42:23.424 line:90%
Your Highness!

00:42:38.105 --> 00:42:39.231 line:90%
A curse.

00:42:43.736 --> 00:42:46.322 line:90%
He was killed by the curse of a spirit.

00:42:47.782 --> 00:42:49.742 line:90%
And the second son of the late King?

00:43:08.177 --> 00:43:09.804 line:90%
<i>A spirit killed him.</i>

00:43:10.679 --> 00:43:13.682 line:90%
The third and fourth brothers as well.
All of them.

00:43:18.396 --> 00:43:23.484 line:90%
<i>Are you sure those princes were killed</i>
<i>by the pond spirit?</i>

00:43:29.365 --> 00:43:30.825 line:90%
What is the matter?

00:43:35.037 --> 00:43:38.624 line:90%
Your Majesty.
Preparations for the hunt are complete.

00:43:38.707 --> 00:43:40.709 line:90%
Prince Yeongan is waiting.

00:43:41.293 --> 00:43:42.336 line:90%
Very well.

00:43:47.716 --> 00:43:49.301 line:90%
We will talk again later.

00:44:39.685 --> 00:44:44.148 line:90%
<i>-He can never know about the pond spirit.</i>
-<i>Stop. I do not wish to hear it.</i>

00:44:44.231 --> 00:44:46.525 line:90%
<i>-You need not know.</i>
<i>-I do not wish to know.</i>

00:44:46.609 --> 00:44:48.235 line:90%
<i>I will wipe out every last seed!</i>

00:44:48.319 --> 00:44:49.320 line:90%
<i>Please, someone.</i>

00:44:49.403 --> 00:44:50.779 line:90%
<i>Admitted to the crime.</i>

00:44:50.863 --> 00:44:51.697 line:90%
<i>Help me.</i>

00:44:51.780 --> 00:44:54.575 line:90%
<i>Do not say</i>
<i>that my own child hears such things.</i>

00:44:54.658 --> 00:44:55.993 line:90%
<i>It is your father who is the</i>…

00:44:59.079 --> 00:44:59.914 line:90%
Why cry again?

00:45:00.998 --> 00:45:02.833 line:90%
More importantly, why are you still here?

00:45:02.917 --> 00:45:04.710 line:90%
There was something I missed.

00:45:05.336 --> 00:45:07.546 line:90%
The one who cursed Prince Yeongan.

00:45:07.630 --> 00:45:09.465 line:90%
It was not
the Most Favored Lady of the Court.

00:45:11.091 --> 00:45:14.470 line:90%
The spirit that clawed at your soul
was not her.

00:45:15.095 --> 00:45:16.096 line:90%
Then…

00:45:17.890 --> 00:45:20.017 line:90%
who was the spirit that tried to kill

00:45:20.809 --> 00:45:22.353 line:90%
Prince Yeongan?

00:45:36.367 --> 00:45:38.327 line:90%
I will take my revenge.

00:45:39.828 --> 00:45:40.871 line:90%
The King

00:45:42.414 --> 00:45:45.918 line:90%
must pay for his sins.

00:45:49.088 --> 00:45:52.091 line:90%
The secret of the royal family…

00:45:52.591 --> 00:45:53.509 line:90%
I will…

00:45:54.593 --> 00:45:58.097 line:90%
I will become the real one.

00:46:00.140 --> 00:46:03.602 line:90%
I will eradicate the royal bloodline!

00:47:24.099 --> 00:47:27.102 line:90%
Prince Yeongan.
We must go to Prince Yeongan!

00:47:28.979 --> 00:47:30.105 line:90%
It is already too late.

00:47:39.823 --> 00:47:40.991 line:90%
Your Highness!

00:47:41.075 --> 00:47:42.618 line:90%
Halt!

00:47:44.244 --> 00:47:46.455 line:90%
Your Highness!

00:47:56.715 --> 00:47:58.133 line:90%
Attend to His Highness at once!

00:47:58.634 --> 00:48:01.428 line:90%
-Your Highness!
-Summon the royal physician!

00:48:03.389 --> 00:48:05.224 line:90%
Then you must leave the palace at once.

00:48:05.307 --> 00:48:06.433 line:90%
Run now.

00:48:06.517 --> 00:48:08.519 line:90%
Since you failed to save Prince Yeongan,

00:48:09.103 --> 00:48:11.271 line:90%
His Majesty will kill you.

00:48:11.855 --> 00:48:13.023 line:90%
If I leave now,

00:48:14.274 --> 00:48:16.568 line:90%
you will die as Prince Yeongan did.

00:48:20.531 --> 00:48:21.949 line:90%
It does not concern you.

00:48:22.032 --> 00:48:22.991 line:90%
Yes, it does.

00:48:23.075 --> 00:48:25.077 line:90%
You saved me.

00:48:25.661 --> 00:48:28.497 line:90%
You risked your life
to cross into the Realm of Gwi for me.

00:48:28.580 --> 00:48:31.166 line:90%
And this time, I will save you.

00:51:31.263 --> 00:51:34.558 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang